00:50:43.332 --> 00:50:53.436
We're ready. Our lamps are full. We're the virgins with our lamps full of oil, anticipating the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:50:53.437 --> 00:51:07.519
Not being like the virgins that would sit by and their lamps weren't full and knew when the bridegroom was coming and said, 'Well, we better go out and buy the oil now.'No, we want to stay in that ready state.

00:51:07.520 --> 00:51:23.476
We want to stay in the ready state, Father, and say, 'Jesus Christ, fill us to capacity overflow,'but not only for just us, but for us to take it to the nations.

00:51:23.477 --> 00:51:35.629
Give me, Father, the glory, the honey glow all around me, God, that when people see me, they see you.

00:51:35.630 --> 00:51:42.959
Help me, Father, to stand in the darkness and people see it and go, 'Man, Lord, you have more.

00:51:42.960 --> 00:51:53.826
You've touched that man. There's something different about that man.'Lord, we thank you, Lord.

00:51:53.827 --> 00:52:08.243
Father, for the Holy Ghost dwells on the inside of us. I know you want to touch them more than we want to touch them.

00:52:08.244 --> 00:52:20.078
I know you want revival more than what we want revival. I know, Father, that you want these souls more than what we want these people to get saved.

00:52:20.079 --> 00:52:24.709
You put it in our heart to even pray what we're praying right now.

00:52:24.710 --> 00:52:31.919
You put it in our heart to even have the desire to want to go pray for these people. It wasn't my idea.

00:52:31.920 --> 00:52:36.192
You gave me the mind to do it and said, 'Brandon, this,'and put the heart in motion.

00:52:36.193 --> 00:52:42.239
I'm telling you, Brandon in himself wouldn't want to do that; it has to be the Holy Spirit to inspire me to do it.

00:52:42.240 --> 00:52:48.928
It has to be the Holy Spirit that inspired me to put this YouTube channel and to pray for you all and do what I do.

00:52:48.929 --> 00:52:55.211
It's the Holy Spirit that does it. So I just thank you that you increase it, Lord. That you increase it.

00:52:55.212 --> 00:53:01.919
I thank you, Father, that we increase it because we know you want it more than us.

00:53:01.920 --> 00:53:09.849
You want to see—you said, 'I want—not one should perish.'Not one should perish, but that all come to repentance.

00:53:09.850 --> 00:53:18.065
All of them. One lady said, 'Well, not everybody's supposed to get saved.'That's not what the Bible says.

00:53:18.066 --> 00:53:35.245
He wants that not one should perish. Not one, but all come to repentance. All. All means all.

00:53:35.246 --> 00:53:43.260
She goes, 'Well, you know, not everybody's going to—'Well, that might be so, but I'm believing God for the best.

00:53:43.261 --> 00:53:49.802
I'm believing for all of them and that God would be able to snatch all of them out of hell.

00:53:49.803 --> 00:53:57.013
He did not make hell for me; he made it for Satan. And I'm not going to participate in something he made for somebody else.

00:53:57.014 --> 00:54:04.598
I'm not taking his 'poo-poo package.'I'm not taking it. He made heaven for me, and I'm going to go to heaven.

00:54:04.599 --> 00:54:07.919
I'm going to be in heaven. I'm going to walk on the streets of gold.

00:54:07.920 --> 00:54:13.861
I'm going to see what Jesus made for me, and I'm going to enjoy it for eternity.

00:54:13.862 --> 00:54:22.465
Glory to God! It's coming. It's coming. Father, we keep our lamps full of oil today.

00:54:22.466 --> 00:54:26.640
We keep our hearts right before you today. We thank you, Lord.

00:54:26.641 --> 00:54:35.105
We thank you, Lord, for the Holy Ghost and the fire on our lives, changing us from the inside out.

00:54:35.106 --> 00:54:47.531
We're going from glory to glory to glory. Amen and amen. Do you all believe that today? Was this encouraging to you? I pray it was.

00:54:47.532 --> 00:54:56.078
I pray this helped you to have some hope, to tell you that you can make it in famine like Isaac.

00:54:56.079 --> 00:55:00.323
I believe, yes, the best is yet to come for the body of Christ.

00:55:00.324 --> 00:55:08.700
Yes, there are dark days for the world, folks. It's going to get so dark that you can touch it.

00:55:08.701 --> 00:55:16.452
It'll be that dark. But we're going to be so light in that darkness that it'll be moths drawn to a light.

00:55:16.453 --> 00:55:20.075
People are going to be drawn to you. But what are they coming for?

00:55:20.076 --> 00:55:27.385
Are they coming for just some religious sermon, or are they going to come and get themselves set free?

00:55:27.386 --> 00:55:39.826
We can teach them old religious Pharisee teaching, or we can tell them the truth of what Jesus Christ did for them.

00:55:39.827 --> 00:55:44.566
There's a lot of religious stuff, but I don't want any part of it.

00:55:44.567 --> 00:55:49.684
All I want to do is be like him. And he wasn't religious at all.

00:55:49.685 --> 00:55:53.753
He ticked the Pharisees off. I want to tick the religious Pharisees off.

00:55:53.755 --> 00:56:03.022
That's why a lot of the people don't want me on their shows to talk to me, because I'm not going to conform to what they want me to do and what they want me to say.

00:56:03.023 --> 00:56:11.772
I'm not scripted. I am not scripted. I will only do what he tells me to do.

00:56:11.773 --> 00:56:22.300
I will not be controlled by religion, and I will not be controlled by Christianity as a whole—modern Christianity, all this that I see out there, TV Christianity.

00:56:22.301 --> 00:56:30.798
I will not be. I will follow the voice of God and I'm radical about it.

00:56:30.799 --> 00:56:41.114
I know I do not fit the normal mold of things; I've been told that recently. But that's all right.

00:56:41.115 --> 00:56:48.806
I want to walk with Jesus and I'll be like John the Baptist, eating locusts and honey in the wilderness, and we're going to get a bunch of people saved and we'll get out of there.

00:56:48.807 --> 00:56:57.986
And when I get on the other side, and you're the janitor and you're cleaning my place, that's fine—because you didn't follow him on this side of the earth.

00:56:57.987 --> 00:57:05.247
What you do on this side affects the other side. Yes, it affects the other side.

00:57:05.248 --> 00:57:19.954
You think that you are such a much over here and you've got this big ego over here—a lot of you, I've seen them—and you think, 'Well, I've arrived and I've got all this going.'But you don't know that the last will be first and the first will be last.

00:57:19.955 --> 00:57:32.766
I keep myself humble before him. Regardless of how people try to pump you up and give you a big head about things, or tear you down, my eyes are only on him.

00:57:32.767 --> 00:57:42.932
Diana's eyes are on him. And that's why it's hard, because you get a lot of religious people that don't like you, especially in leadership, and they make it known.

00:57:42.933 --> 00:57:52.136
But that's all right. I say, 'Hey, I walk in love and we follow Jesus.'We follow Jesus, and you don't have to put me on your show.

00:57:52.137 --> 00:57:57.598
You don't have to do that because I only want to be where Jesus wants me.

00:57:57.599 --> 00:58:03.037
You know, it's interesting. I will not be in the mold of what people try to put me in.

00:58:03.038 --> 00:58:12.756
'You do what we tell you to do. You say what we tell you to say.'Oh no, we will do what Jesus says to say.

00:58:12.757 --> 00:58:19.039
And if you don't like that, that's fine. You didn't want me on anyway.

00:58:19.040 --> 00:58:22.851
You let the Holy Ghost move. Yes. And a lot of people don't want that.

00:58:22.852 --> 00:58:36.446
And I thought they did. I thought a lot more people did. Boy, were we fooled.

00:58:36.447 --> 00:58:43.176
Praise the Lord. I don't know why I said all that, but it is what it is.

00:58:43.177 --> 00:58:54.318
Click the subscribe button. Show the world that we're alive and we're there. Show them that the Christians mean business.

00:58:54.319 --> 00:59:00.896
By you making YouTube channels grow like this, it shows the world that this is what you're wanting to hear.

00:59:00.897 --> 00:59:05.619
The more the world's channels grow, they go, 'See? That's what they want.

00:59:05.620 --> 00:59:13.517
Advertise on those channels.'Don't do it over here. This is us saying something. This is us sticking together.

00:59:13.518 --> 00:59:21.999
You subscribing and clicking the notification bell—you're saying we want more content like this.

00:59:22.000 --> 00:59:39.838
We want people like that praying and helping pray for their nation, versus whoever these—I'm not going to name a secular channel that's growing huge, you know, and they've got 100 million subscribers or 10 million and you go, 'Wow.'And all they talk about is trash.

00:59:39.839 --> 00:59:42.974
I want to talk about Jesus. And I appreciate you being here today.

00:59:42.975 --> 00:59:47.536
I truly do. I appreciate your support. Comment something nice down below for the algorithm.

00:59:47.537 --> 00:59:56.822
And we appreciate it, y'all. It really does help. God bless you all and we just want to thank you.

00:59:56.823 --> 01:00:01.199
Thank you for being here today. Well, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

01:00:01.200 --> 01:00:08.930
Jesus loves you so much and we love you. God bless you all and we will see you again soon. Bye-bye.

